msgid "Kolf"
msgstr "Kolf"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kolf.appdata.xml:10
msgid "Miniature Golf"
msgstr "Minigolfs"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kolf.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"Kolf is a miniature golf game. The game is played from an overhead view, "
"with a short bar representing the golf club. Kolf features many different "
"types of objects, such water hazards, slopes, sand traps, and black holes "
"(warps), among others."
msgstr ""
"„Kolf“ ir minigolfa spēle. To spēlē augšskatā, kurā īsa josla reprezentē "
"golfa nūju. „Kolf“ izmanto daudzus dažāda veida objektus, piemēram, ūdeni, "
"slīpumus, smilšu slazdus, melnos caurumus (teleportācija) un citus."

